# Quantumult X RuleSet - Bytedance.list (Force PROXY)
# Repo: Jovanykoch/Jovanykoch.github.io
# Updated: 2026-04-03
#
# Usage (Quantumult X):
# [filter_remote]
# https://jkoch14.me/qx/Bytedance.list, tag=Bytedance.list, force-policy=PROXY, update-interval=86400, opt-parser=false, enabled=true
#
# Notes:
# - Put this list ABOVE china.list if you also use china.list (DIRECT), to avoid being overridden.

# -----------------------
# Douyin core
# -----------------------
host-suffix,douyin.com
host-suffix,iesdouyin.com
host-suffix,douyinpic.com
host-suffix,douyinstatic.com
host-suffix,douyincdn.com
host-suffix,douyinliving.com

# -----------------------
# ByteDance app platform
# -----------------------
host-suffix,snssdk.com
host-suffix,amemv.com

# -----------------------
# ByteDance core / common APIs
# -----------------------
host-suffix,bytedance.com
host-suffix,byted.org
host-suffix,byteimg.com
host-suffix,bytecdn.cn
host-suffix,bytegoofy.com
host-suffix,bytegecko.com
host-suffix,bytescm.com
host-suffix,bytetcc.com
host-suffix,zijieapi.com
host-suffix,zijieimg.com

# Shared content family
host-suffix,toutiao.com
host-suffix,ixigua.com

# -----------------------
# Volcengine / ByteDance Cloud
# -----------------------
host-suffix,volcengine.com
host-suffix,volces.com
host-suffix,volccdn.com
host-suffix,volccdn1.com
host-suffix,volccdn2.com
host-suffix,volccdn3.com

# -----------------------
# IES CDN domains
# -----------------------
host-suffix,iescdn.com
host-suffix,iesimg.com